- For k=3, total is 1 + 3(3)(2) = 19
   - 1, [2-4], [5-10], [11-19] (Counts are 19 numbers)
- For k=4, total is 1 + 3(4)(3) = 37
   - 1, [2-4], [5-10], [11-19], [20-37] (Counts are 37 numbers)
